{"tid":455583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法】馬迷稱影響入場意欲 學生憂港制度政治化","createTime":"2017-11-02T08:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T10:55:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"564e3264eab2452fdb7ab5e47fc4ed56e5bf3c41","tid":455583,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"《國歌法》即將列入《基本法》附件三，正在訪京的大律師馬恩國更引述基本法委員會主任李飛言論，指未來馬場奏國歌時，場內的馬迷亦須站立，否則有機會被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n不過有馬迷則認為李飛說法並不合理，間中會到馬場的馬迷黃先生稱，馬場屬娛樂場所，難以要求市民在此環境下仍然莊嚴地對待國歌，「啲人賭錢都賭到亂曬龍！邊個會理國歌？」他又稱，引入《國歌法》無疑會影響馬迷入場意欲。<br />\n<br />\n而有學生亦認明現時的國法化只會淪為當權者用作政治打壓的工具。就讀中六級的黃同學表示，學校每年都有一天會舉行升旗禮，但自己都曾耳聞有同學噓國歌。他憂慮未來立法，在校內噓國歌的同學會被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，不贊成現行的國歌法，因為其對侮辱國歌的定義並不如《國旗法》般清晰，「如果我奏國歌時背向國旗，咁樣都算侮辱？」他續指，在法例對侮辱行為定義含糊的情況下，警察作政治檢控時會「take advantage 」（有優勢），他形容《國歌法》會進一步把香港「制度政治化」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171102/large/1509609166_765c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171102%2Flarge%2F1509609166_765c.jpg&h=82b41a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬迷黃先生認為馬場屬娛樂場所，難要求市民在此環境下仍莊嚴地對待國歌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171102/large/1509609204_8f00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171102%2Flarge%2F1509609204_8f00.jpg&h=b0854d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中六生黃同學指曾在校內耳聞有同學噓國歌，憂未來立法後那些同學會被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171102/57408520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F57408520&d=Od93XWp5wLOUKSfcqLyypJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b4415696\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F57408520&h=d76e40a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171102/57408520</a>"},{"pid":"eb0d37723a39f0d9651fcfb1353a2737982e311c","tid":455583,"uid":43042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"當一個城市變到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細字版<br />\n________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人簽名</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">五毛/假膠一律統稱中囯人<br />\n<br />\n假膠唔係五毛，但就做緊五毛一樣嘅事，以前大事大非面前絕對唔會玩嘢，但宜家佢地咩時候都仲扮鬼扮馬，搞到分唔清邊個打邊個，佢地已經走火入魔，所以喺以後逢見假膠請一律認作五毛處理<br />\n<br />\n由於中囯人再次泛濫，現列出部分人渣名錄，比大家留意返相關人渣，如有遺漏希望大家增補，對抗中国人一齊努力<br />\n<br />\n最新名錄(定期更新)：<br />\n<br />\n-李尋歡- <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#67878 (小李探花李尋歡)<br />\n潮吹口爆糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #3066<br />\n精神錯亂最佳代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#62391<br />\n兔仔有愛情嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #58099(高葵株式會社)<br />\n大鵬金翅神將 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #64806<br />\nJR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #86841<br />\n高登色狼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#14482<br />\n三色貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #46644<br />\n香港鍵國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #50533（精英連登仔）<br />\n熱血藍絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #48442<br />\n角大不角細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#72990<br />\n一齊攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #33874<br />\n西門慶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #102056<br />\n連泥往 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #41116<br />\n十五天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#57952<br />\n揾嚟搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #122718<br />\n立法會已完<img src=\"/as